GOD FUCKING DAMN IT!

Not to sound like a smug self important asshole, but you know what is one of the definite downsides to being smart: whenever someone doesn't fucking listen to you about important life saving shit just to spite you.

My mom didn't listen to me about how you're not supposed to sleep facing up while drunk and thank god she woke up from vomiting otherwise she would have joined done a Jimi Hendrix.

No matter how smug or argumentative someone is if they say the phrase "if you don't listen to me you will literally die" maybe you should fucking listen.

When you eventually die you don't want your last words to be "you're not the boss of me!"/"you can't tell me what to do!"
